Difference between cloud native application and traditional application

   Cloud Native Application               Traditional Application
  ______________________________________________________________________
i)  Predictable Behaviour                   Unpredictable Behaviour

ii)  OS Abstarction                          OS Dependent

iii)  Rapid Recovery                          Slow Recovery

iv)  Continuous Delivery                     Waterfall Model

v)  Right sized capacity                    Oversized and Dependent
    and Independent    
